@NODE a "Install GoldEd APIs"

 -Copy whole drawer IconsMF to Golded:API/DOCK/
 -Copy DockMF.prefs DockMF.api to Golded:API/Dock/
 -Select "Config/API" from Menu
 -Click on Load and select file "DockMF.api" (see above)
 -Finished!
@ENDNODE
