@ENDNODE
@NODE d "PT-Prefs"

 PT-Prefs lets you change the lookout of your Pro/Star/Noise/Soundtracker.
 Its converts Main Screen,Font and the Pointer to standart IFF-ILBM Pictures,
 which can be edited by you with your favourite paint-program and patches
 them back into the tracker binary.
@ENDNODE
